headline: Accenture (ACN): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Accenture’s shares (currently trading at $294.75) have posted a disappointing 18.8% loss while the S&P 500 was down 5%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
